QuestData.Title: The Essence of G'huun
QuestData.Description:
Analysis of blood-infused bones complete. Will be able to create synthetic essence similar to G'huun.
Will take a moment to apply essence, allow you to walk past undead without combat.
Must hurry. More forces of G'huun are around temple. Must get inside to reactivate containment protocols.
QuestData.LogDescription: Have Titan Keeper Hezrel apply Synthetic Essence to allow safe passage past undead.
